{"article_id":"ZkcJyunGxkw3HeuC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump 's attorney general is now being drawn into the investigations of Russian election meddling .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Jeff Sessions will testify publicly tomorrow to the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and he may have to answer questions","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"raised by last week 's testimony from James Comey .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The president attacked the fired FBI director again Sunday","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"tweeting ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"`` I believe","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"the James Comey leaks will be far more prevalent","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"than anyone ever thought possible .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Totally illegal","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"-- very cowardly . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"A lot of questions for Sessions cropped up after Comey 's testimony last week .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Senators from both sides want to know","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"why Sessions was involved in the FBI director 's firing ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"reports ' Nancy Cordes .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"On `` Face the Nation '' Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer ran through the questions","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"he wants answered by the attorney general .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham :","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Trump 's `` wrestling match '' with Comey interferes with U.S. agenda","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"`` Did he interfere with the Russian investigation","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"before he recused himself ?","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The president said","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Comey was fired","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"because of Russia .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"How does that fit in with his recusal ? ''","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Sessions was scheduled to testify before the Judiciary Committee tomorrow","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"-- about the Department of Justice budget .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"But he announced the switch to the intelligence committee this weekend","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"after it became clear that he was only going to get grilled about his role in Comey 's firing .","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"Sessions recused himself from the Russia investigation over three months ago ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"after admitting","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"he had not disclosed two meetings with the Russian ambassador in 2016 .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Comey suggested to senators last week","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that there might be more to it than that .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"`` We also were aware of facts","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that I ca n't discuss in an open setting","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that would make his continued engagement in a Russia-related investigation problematic , ''","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Comey said during last week 's testimony .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"As for the president 's offer","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"to give his side of the story under oath ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Republican Lindsey Graham urged the president Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"`` Do n't do it ! ''","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"He warned Mr. Trump","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"that he might be , `` his own worst enemy . ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"`` You may be the first president in history","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"to go down","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"because you ca n't stop inappropriately talking about an investigation","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"if you just were quiet ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"would clear you , ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Graham said on `` Face the Nation '' over the weekend .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Some Republicans now are arguing","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"that Sessions is n't the first attorney general","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"to inject politics in an investigation ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"pointing to testimony last week","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"that Loretta Lynch urged Comey to call the probe into Clinton 's e-mail practice a `` matter '' rather than `` investigation . ''","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Democrat Senator Dianne Feinstein said","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"that request made her `` queasy . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":117,"left":84,"right":116,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":84,"left":69,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":0,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":61,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":1,"right":60,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":60,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":4,"right":66,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":5,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":63,"left":6,"right":62,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":62,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":83,"left":74,"right":82,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":11,"right":71,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":75,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":81,"left":76,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration